1. Project Identity & Scope Lock
1.1 Purpose

Ergalyon v2 is a dedicated Invoice and Offer Processing System for B2B tool and consumable wholesalers. It ingests supplier invoices/offers, extracts product and pricing data, matches them to internal product identities, enriches them with technical characteristics, and exports structured data to update internal cost prices.

1.2 In-Scope (MUST)
Upload and parsing of Invoices (PDF, scanned image, Excel/XML) from suppliers.
Upload and parsing of Offers (PDF, scanned image, Excel/XML) from suppliers.
Supplier Management: Full CRUD, soft-delete, complete supplier card (AADE data, contacts, agreements).
Product Management: Internal product identity management (independent of supplier codes).
Intelligent Parsing: Multi-layered extraction (Hardcoded Parsers → Dynamic Parsers → AI Vision/OCR).
Normalization: Supplier-specific code transformations (e.g., Poimenidis 03- stripping).
Cost Price Update: Updating product cost based on parsed invoice data, with user-controlled overwrite.
Enrichment (5 Levels):
Invoice XML/embedded data.
Supplier Catalog files (manually uploaded).
Supplier Product Lists (manually uploaded).
Manual entry/correction by user.
Web Scraping (last resort) via Crawl4AI for images, descriptions, barcodes.
Export: Generation of XLSX files compatible with Pylon ERP (Import/Update modes).
Multi-tenancy: Full data isolation between organizations/companies.
Audit & History: Complete logs of who changed what and when.
1.3 Out-of-Scope (NEVER)
Supplier Agreement Comparison: The system will NOT compare uploaded supplier agreements with invoice data to validate terms. Agreements are for archival and chat search ONLY.
Pylon Code Matching: The system will NOT use the internal Pylon ERP code (PYLONCODE) during the product matching phase. Matching is based on Supplier Code, Manufacturer Code, Barcode, and Description.
ERP Write-Back Integration: The system generates an XLSX file. It does NOT push data directly into Pylon ERP via API.
E-shop Functions: No connection to the Magento 2 e-shop project.
Dispute/Compliance Engine: No automated flagging of invoice discrepancies against agreements.
Email Drafting: No AI-generated emails to suppliers.
1.4 Target User
Primary: Purchasing managers and accountants in tool/consumable wholesale companies.
Language: Greek (el-GR) only. No multi-language support.
