12. Appendix
12.1 Glossary
AADE: Ανεξάρτητη Αρχή Δημοσίων Εσόδων (Greek Tax Authority).
AFM: Αριθμός Φορολογικού Μητρώου (Tax ID).
Enrichment: The process of adding missing data (images, specs, barcodes) to a product.
Matching: Linking an invoice line item to an existing internal product identity.
Normalization: Transforming supplier-specific codes into a canonical format.
Offer: A quotation or price list from a supplier (not a fiscal invoice).
Pylon: The ERP system used by the company.
RAG: Retrieval-Augmented Generation (chat with documents).
Soft Delete: Marking a record as deleted without physically removing it.
